	<p>Want more sites? Read <a href="https://varyingvagrantvagrants.org/docs/en-US/adding-a-new-site/">how to add a new site</a> or <a href="https://varyingvagrantvagrants.org/docs/en-US/adding-a-new-site/adding-an-existing-site/">how to add existing sites</a>. To disable a site just remove its entry from <code>config/config.yml</code> then reprovision with <code>vagrant up --provision</code>. You can also set <code>skip_provisioning: true</code></p>
